<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Score">Score</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Departed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Score">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>The <a href="/wiki/Film_score" title="Film score">film score</a> for <i>The Departed</i> was written by <a href="/wiki/Howard_Shore" title="Howard Shore">Howard Shore</a> and performed by guitarists <a href="/wiki/Sharon_Isbin" title="Sharon Isbin">Sharon Isbin</a>, <a href="/wiki/G._E._Smith" title="G. E. Smith">G. E. Smith</a>, Larry Saltzman and <a href="/wiki/Marc_Ribot" title="Marc Ribot">Marc Ribot</a>. The score was recorded in Shore's own studio in <a href="/wiki/New_York_State" title="New York State" class="mw-redirect">New York State</a>. The album, <i>The Departed: Original Score</i>, was released December 5, 2006 by <a href="/wiki/New_Line" title="New Line" class="mw-redirect">New Line</a>, and produced by Jason Cienkus.</p>
